            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion and garlic have softened, add your <strong>tomato paste</strong> and <strong>dried thyme</strong> and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add 250ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[325ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[350ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> with your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> and <strong>red wine vinegar</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Reduce the heat to medium-low and cook for 5 min or until the sauce has slightly thickened – this is your <strong>tomato sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
