    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>aubergine & courgette ratatouille</strong> next to the <strong>cooked rice</strong> and top with the <strong>grated cheese</strong></p><p>Season with a generous grind of<strong> black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
